## agentmesh

Synchronize repository intelligence across AI coding runtimes

Usage: agentmesh [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  status          Fast snapshot of current state
  scan            Report detected runtimes and entities without writing
  init            Set up AgentMesh in a repository
  install         Install sync hooks
  sync            Run a sync pass
  diff            Show what sync would change
  apply           Apply pending changes from a previous diff
  doctor          Run deep health checks
  restore         Restore a preserved runtime version
  ack             Acknowledge pending conflict resolution
  watch           Run the low-level watcher daemon
  upgrade         Repin integrity to the current binary
  start           Start AgentMesh for this repository by restoring local hooks
  stop            Stop AgentMesh for this repository and keep shared state
  uninstall       Remove AgentMesh-owned state from this repository
  reconcile-lock  Recover from a textual lockfile merge conflict
  help            Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --silent         Suppress informational output
      --no-color       Disable ANSI color output
      --color <COLOR>  Override color behavior [default: auto] [possible values: auto, always, never]
      --cwd <CWD>      Run as if invoked from this directory
  -v, --verbose...     Increase output detail
  -h, --help           Print help
  -V, --version        Print version


## agentmesh status

Fast snapshot of current state

Usage: status [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --json  Emit machine-readable JSON
  -h, --help  Print help


## agentmesh scan

Report detected runtimes and entities without writing

Usage: scan [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --json  Emit machine-readable JSON
  -h, --help  Print help


## agentmesh init

Set up AgentMesh in a repository

Usage: init [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --canonical-instructions <CANONICAL_INSTRUCTIONS>
          Resolve divergent root instructions non-interactively [possible values: AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md]
  -y, --yes
          Skip confirmation prompts
      --dry-run
          Print planned actions without writing
      --skip-hooks
          Skip runtime hook installation
  -h, --help
          Print help


## agentmesh install

Install sync hooks

Usage: install [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --runtime <RUNTIME>  Runtime whose hooks should be installed
      --git-pre-commit     Install the git pre-commit safety-net hook
      --force              Install despite a managed existing pre-commit hook
  -y, --yes                Skip confirmation prompts
      --dry-run            Print planned actions without writing
  -h, --help               Print help


## agentmesh sync

Run a sync pass

Usage: sync [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --check              Report drift without writing
      --await-drain        Block until the pending queue is empty
      --trigger <TRIGGER>  Identify the call origin
  -h, --help               Print help


## agentmesh diff

Show what sync would change

Usage: diff [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --json  Emit machine-readable JSON
  -h, --help  Print help


## agentmesh apply

Apply pending changes from a previous diff

Usage: apply

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help


## agentmesh doctor

Run deep health checks

Usage: doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --versions        Print version information only
      --integrity-only  Verify integrity only
      --watcher-only    Show watcher status only
      --json            Emit machine-readable JSON
  -h, --help            Print help


## agentmesh restore

Restore a preserved runtime version

Usage: restore [OPTIONS] --from <FROM> <ID>

Arguments:
  <ID>  Entity identifier to restore

Options:
      --from <FROM>  Runtime whose preserved version should be restored
      --at <AT>      Specific preserved timestamp
      --dry-run      Print planned actions without writing
  -y, --yes          Skip confirmation prompts
  -h, --help         Print help


## agentmesh ack

Acknowledge pending conflict resolution

Usage: ack [OPTIONS] [ID]

Arguments:
  [ID]  Entity identifier to acknowledge. Omit to acknowledge all

Options:
  -y, --yes   Skip confirmation prompts
  -h, --help  Print help


## agentmesh watch

Run the low-level watcher daemon

Usage: watch [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --persistent           Do not idle-exit
      --register-as-service  Register the watcher as a system service
      --foreground           Run in the foreground
  -y, --yes                  Skip confirmation prompts
  -h, --help                 Print help


